OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1779354384
OL,3,CWelsh hospital stops accepting A&E
OL,4,Cpatients due to water shortage
OL,6,FThe Princess of Wales Hospital in
OL,7,FBridgend said it is not accepting
OL,8,Fpatients into its emergency department
OL,9,Fon Tuesday (19 May) evening after
OL,10,Fdisruption to the site's water supply.
OL,12,FThe health board said it was
OL,13,F"experiencing significant temporary
OL,14,Fdisruption to the water supply" but
OL,15,Fwas trying to resolve the issue.
OL,17,FIt advised people to attend another
OL,18,Fhospital if they need urgent medical
OL,19,Fattention.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/5
