OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1779354384
OL,3,CWelsh hospital stops accepting A&E
OL,4,Cpatients due to water shortage
OL,6,FIn a statement posted on Cwm Taf
OL,7,FMorgannwg University Health Board's
OL,8,Fwebsite, they said: "We are
OL,9,Fexperiencing significant temporary
OL,10,Fdisruption to the water supply at
OL,11,FPrincess of Wales Hospital.
OL,13,F"Due to a water shortage, we are
OL,14,Fcurrently unable to accept patients
OL,15,Finto the Emergency Department this
OL,16,Fevening while we work to resolve the
OL,17,Fissue.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/5
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1779354384
OL,3,CWelsh hospital stops accepting A&E
OL,4,Cpatients due to water shortage
OL,6,F"Please do not attend the Emergency
OL,7,FDepartment at Princess of Wales
OL,8,FHospital unless absolutely necessary.
OL,9,FIf you need urgent or emergency care,
OL,10,Fplease attend another hospital
OL,11,Fwherever possible."
OL,13,FThe hospital will also not be
OL,14,Faccepting visitors on Tuesday evening.
OL,16,FThe health board added: "We are
OL,17,Fworking closely with Dwr Cymru Welsh
OL,18,FWater to restore services as quickly
OL,19,Fas possible.
OL,26,@yD@Ws{
