CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1779354384
OL,3,CWelsh hospital stops accepting A&E
OL,4,Cpatients due to water shortage
OL,6,F"We will keep you updated as soon as
OL,7,Ffurther information becomes available.
OL,9,F"Thank you for your patience and
OL,10,Funderstanding."
OL,12,FThe closest A&E to the Princess of
OL,13,FWales Hospital is around half an hour
OL,14,Faway, in Llantrisant at the Royal
OL,15,FGlamorgan Hospital.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/5
